{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1974,"month":1,"day":13}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"幸福泉","authors":["安造计"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"野营来到阎家坝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"访贫问苦银灯下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士提起幸福泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一语引出万句话……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阎家坝自古打不出水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三、四里外把水拉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大姑娘经常洗不上脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老奶奶做饭锅难刷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风一刮砂石飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒下种子难发芽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放前，死亡线上苦煎熬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放后，落后帽子摘不下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们奋起把井打；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少次，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑风吹断打井架……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命号声急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风吹遍阎家坝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大批判杀得黑风退，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷山村开放大寨花！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋战三夏又三冬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马不卸鞍人不乏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凿穿万丈老龙脉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村头竖起大水塔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器一响清水流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙头一拧水哗哗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲净了污泥和浊水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"医好了旧社会留下的老伤疤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流水欢歌唱不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干旱灾难连根拔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒草坡变成米粮川，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乱石窝变成金银洼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾苗喜迎春风长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉花笑对秋风发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年跃进过“黄河”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年又把“长江”跨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席开出幸福泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"散作千溪遍万家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大寨红花遍地开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国大地美如画……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士静听心潮急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灌一壶清水随身挎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看一眼，踏遍千山不知累，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝一口，闪电雷霆眼不眨！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}